://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZ7hFQE.gif&h=d7f5bbf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe369527f0d4b8a5fe49226ad64fde79c2508d5a","tid":1667923,"uid":293901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"590aa047c992050cc410e38b6f8a95fe3560f248","tid":1667923,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:27:57.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"bef9de9e41fa159b42e66ce0df632e4658947b88","tid":1667923,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9bde8cb4d06bc9b763a06002d620e465e0b8233","tid":1667923,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5eoBnM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5eoBnM.jpg&h=b81ba04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推埋上reddit twitter <br />\n<br />\n我地會幫鴿鴿沖涼 佢地就mask都唔比狗帶<br />\n比全世界知我地同黨察分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"狗唔會襲擊養佢嘅主人，警賊會襲擊養佢嘅市民。"}]}